t_video_library::text_card_0::text: Seenaa suur-sagalee gaarii qopheessuun muraalee garagaraa haammata. Qajoojiin kun seenaawwan garagaraa himuuf muraalee barbaaddu argachuuf si qajeelcha.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[30: Yeroo gaafannoo geggeessuuf gaafattutti waa'ee matadureekee yookaan galmakee ifa godhi.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[10: Waraabbiin seeraan qophaa'e bakka qaamichi irra garagalee jiru yookaan irra deemuuf hambisa.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[56: Sagaleen suur-sagalee keessatti walakkaa odeeffannooti, waraabbii kamiifuu yaada keessa galchi.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[65: Waa'ee seenaa taatechaa yookaan maalii akka ta'u irratti haqaawwan hawwatoo tokko tokko nutti himi.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[24: Hamma dandeesse sagaleekee xinneessii fayyadami, seenaakee karaa sagalee namootaa himi.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[38: Bakka gaarii irraa waraabdu mirkaneeffachuudhaan goodaayyaakee hamma xumuraatti achitti qabi.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[39: Hafuurakee hin qabatin, waraabbiikee waraabuuf qopheessiitii hafuura baafadhu. Yeroo qophooftetti waraabuu jalqabi.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[36: Waraabduurratti cuqaasuukeen dura sagalee duubaa jeequudhaan qulqullina seenaakee miidhuu danda'u dhaggeeffadhu.
t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[55: Ifi tilmaamaan qaamicharraa fageenya meetira 1 irra jiru baayyee gaariidha.

t_video_library::tip_collection::tips[29: Yeroo danda'ametti jalqabarratti waan argitee fi gaaffiif deebii waraabi.
